  "detailed_description": "<h1>Development & Feedback Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837190/extras/1e440d1abe5b6bd59490bc809251913a.avif?t=1722821173\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Select Classes and Talents that compliment your playstyle such as Builder or Mage, unlock more classes & talents by completing objectives.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837190/extras/a52cd6161a0623420a0efef8e94b7117.avif?t=1722821173\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Unlock new towers and upgrade them to improve their stats. Improve attack towers with other towers or buffs to create devastating effects<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837190/extras/0c15510ad41c39e30723856bf02654a0.avif?t=1722821173\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Cast down powers on invaders to deal massive damage with meteors, lightning strikes, overcharges, and more..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837190/extras/0789f117419ed032b195525647b2983c.avif?t=1722821173\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Create an endless number of custom worlds, play through the included levels, or enjoy those created and shared by others.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837190/extras/1e440d1abe5b6bd59490bc809251913a.avif?t=1722821173\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Select Classes and Talents that compliment your playstyle such as Builder or Mage, unlock more classes & talents by completing objectives.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837190/extras/a52cd6161a0623420a0efef8e94b7117.avif?t=1722821173\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Unlock new towers and upgrade them to improve their stats. Improve attack towers with other towers or buffs to create devastating effects<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837190/extras/0c15510ad41c39e30723856bf02654a0.avif?t=1722821173\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Cast down powers on invaders to deal massive damage with meteors, lightning strikes, overcharges, and more..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1837190/extras/0789f117419ed032b195525647b2983c.avif?t=1722821173\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Create an endless number of custom worlds, play through the included levels, or enjoy those created and shared by others.",
